				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The Staves of Elemental Mastery <span style="font-weight: bold">all add at least 350 hp</span> to their respective pets, at all levels they work at, 49 - 60.  The only staff I have not been able to test is the Air staff.
<br />

<br />

<br />
At level 49, the Fire and Air pets appear to have ~350 hp above what their low level focus items give them.  
<br />

<br />
The Earth pet merely gains ~350 hp, where it gained none from its original focus.
<br />

<br />
They all raise the pets level by 1, <span style="font-style: italic">except for the Fire staff on the level 58 fire pet which doesn't raise the level at all</span>.  They all raise melee damage by 2, <span style="font-style: italic">except for the Fire staff, which raises melee damage by 3 for the 52/58 pets only</span>.  This puts the 52 pet at 39 melee damage, and the 58 pet at 51 maxmelee damage.
<br />

<br />

<br />
All the hp numbers posted above, +350, are very close to my tested values.  The focused 57 Earth pet appears to have around 3650 hp, The focused 49 Earth appears to have around 3500 hp, the focused 49 fire pet appears to have around 2450 hp, etc., etc..<br />_________________<br />Arhallia Ironborne
<br />

<br />
Alliance of the Arcane
<br />
Quellious server</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
